{"_path":"/tags/textformats/xsl","_dir":"textformats","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"XSL","description":"XSL 家族的语言提供了丰富的工具和技术，用于 XML 文档的转换、呈现和格式化，适用于各种应用场景，从简单的数据转换到复杂的文档排版和打印输出。","name":"xsl","icon":"devicon:xml","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"xsl"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XSL"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"icon","props":{"className":["size-32"],"name":"devicon:xml"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XSL（Extensible Stylesheet Language）是一种用于 XML 文档转换和呈现的语言。它由三个部分组成："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_1-xsltxsl-transformations"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. XSLT（XSL Transformations）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XSLT 是 XSL 的一部分，用于将 XML 文档转换成其他格式，如 HTML、XML 或纯文本。XSLT 使用一种基于模板和模式匹配的声明性编程风格。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要特点和用途"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要特点和用途："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模板匹配和转换："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 使用模板来匹配 XML 文档的元素，并生成输出结果。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XPath 表达式："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 使用 XPath 语言来选择和操作 XML 文档中的节点。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"变量和函数："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 支持变量和函数的定义，增强了转换的灵活性和复用性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"递归处理和条件分支："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 支持递归处理和条件分支，可以根据需要动态调整转换逻辑。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2-xpathxml-path-language"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. XPath（XML Path Language）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XPath 是 XSLT 的一部分，用于在 XML 文档中定位和选择节点。它提供了一组表达式，允许开发者通过路径或模式来访问 XML 文档的各个部分。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要特点和用途-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要特点和用途："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"路径表达式："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 使用路径表达式描述节点在文档中的位置，类似于文件系统路径。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"谓词："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 可以使用谓词来过滤节点，根据特定条件选择节点。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"函数库："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 提供了一系列内置函数，用于在 XPath 表达式中执行字符串操作、数学计算、日期处理等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"轴："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 支持不同类型的轴，如子节点、父节点、兄弟节点等，扩展了节点选择的灵活性。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_3-xsl-foxsl-formatting-objects"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. XSL-FO（XSL Formatting Objects）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"XSL-FO 是 XSL 的另一部分，用于定义文档的格式化和排版规则，以便生成输出的打印或显示形式。XSL-FO 主要用于描述文档的外观和样式，如页面布局、文本格式、图像和表格等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要特点和用途-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要特点和用途："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"页面序列和布局："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 定义页面的顺序、页眉页脚、页面边距等布局属性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"块和行内对象："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 描述文本块、图像、表格和其他对象的布局和样式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"属性和属性集："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 使用属性和属性集来设置对象的格式、间距和对齐方式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多语言支持："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 提供多语言文本的处理和排版能力，支持不同语言和文化的排版需求。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"使用场景"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用场景："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据转换和整合："}]},{"type":"text","value":" XSLT 用于将 XML 数据转换成不同格式，如 HTML 或其他 XML 结构，适用于数据交换和整合。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"动态网页生成："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 结合 XSLT 和 XPath 可以根据 XML 数据生成动态网页内容。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"打印和报告生成："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 使用 XSL-FO 可以生成具有复杂格式和布局要求的打印输出或电子报告。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据查询和分析："}]},{"type":"text","value":" XPath 可用于查询和分析 XML 数据，从中提取有用信息或执行计算。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总之，XSL 家族的语言提供了丰富的工具和技术，用于 XML 文档的转换、呈现和格式化，适用于各种应用场景，从简单的数据转换到复杂的文档排版和打印输出。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":5,"depth":5,"links":[{"id":"xsl","depth":2,"text":"XSL","children":[{"id":"_1-xsltxsl-transformations","depth":3,"text":"1. XSLT（XSL Transformations）","children":[{"id":"主要特点和用途","depth":4,"text":"主要特点和用途："}]},{"id":"_2-xpathxml-path-language","depth":3,"text":"2. XPath（XML Path Language）","children":[{"id":"主要特点和用途-1","depth":4,"text":"主要特点和用途："}]},{"id":"_3-xsl-foxsl-formatting-objects","depth":3,"text":"3. XSL-FO（XSL Formatting Objects）","children":[{"id":"主要特点和用途-2","depth":4,"text":"主要特点和用途："}]},{"id":"使用场景","depth":3,"text":"使用场景："}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:tags:textformats:xsl.md","_source":"content","_file":"tags/textformats/xsl.md","_extension":"md"}